1️⃣ Discovery (Homepage → Browsing)

User lands on the homepage
Sees a featured packages and btc Maps/Bitcoin businesses
Clicks “View Packages”
2️⃣ Choosing a Package (Packages Page → Checkout)
User explores travel options
Selects a package → Clicks “Book with Bitcoin”
3️⃣ Payment (Bitcoin Checkout)
User pays via Lightning (LNURL) or on-chain BTC
Payment confirmed via Nostr or email
Receives trip details & itinerary
4️⃣ Experience (Arrives in Madeira, Uses Bitcoin)
Uses MadTrips’ Bitcoin Map to find places to eat, shop, and explore
Checks into locations & shares experiences on Nostr